Berkshire Hathaway HomeServices Carolina Premier Properties

data.description: This home is perfect for those looking for an open floor plan living space without the restrictions of an HOA or city taxes. The location, just 10 minutes from MCAS New River Air Station, makes it a great option for military families or anyone who wants to be close to the base. Inside, you'll find three bedrooms and two full bathrooms, providing plenty of room for families or guests. The home itself has been recently painted and features a modern tiled shower in the master bathroom, a huge kitchen island and so much more. The corner lot provides ample space for children and pets to play or for outdoor entertaining.The one-car garage offers additional storage and parking space.Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this wonderful home yours. Don't wait, schedule a showing today!
